rComments: Paolo is the best professor I've ever met at University! He gives detailed feedback and he encouraged me a lot during the journey! I am so sad that he only taught us for the first semester...
The best prof I've had in uni, really changed my language learning experience for the better.
Amazing lectures! Paolo is so helpful and will do the extra work to help you if you are struggling. He is clear and concise, he always stayed after class to further explain a concept

Paolo's lecture are clear and he makes the material very approachable.  Also makes a point to get everyone to participate; he truly cares about the students.  Definitely one of the best instructors I've had in undergrad.
Made 9am class fun, always willing to go the extra step to help you out, makes an effort to get to know all his students. My best prof in first year, hands down.
